<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-10-0960 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report contains the committee reports submitted at the annual meetingon nuclear technology in 1986 at Aachen on the subject of HTR materialdevelopment, supply and removal. Component design specific to HTR's,development of material for advanced HTR plant, manufacture and testingof fuel elements, experiments and calculations for fission product releasedue to accidents, manufacture and testing of graphite and achieving fuelremoval from HTR's are dealt with in detail. (HAG).</TEXT></DOC>